data.description: Located in the Central Hillside neighborhood, this residence not only embodies the charm of a traditional home but also places you within easy reach of Duluth's vibrant community and amenities. Embrace the perfect blend of modern flooring, layout, and paint along with timeless character in this enchanting property. This property showcases two bedrooms on the second story of the home, each with unique details that capture the essence of the home's traditional design. The bathroom, has a classic claw foot tub on the main level of the home, right off of the kitchen. Take your pick whether entertaining in the fenced-in backyard or in the park conveniently located next to the property. There is loads of space for your entertaining desires. Outside, you'll find a quaint front porch, solid back deck, backyard fencing, along with patio pavers in the backyard. Modern updates include a newer furnace, roof, decking and siding. Come take a tour of your new home today!
